  "message": "test(fft): raise differential coverage on irfft/hfft/ihfft/rfft2/irfft2/ifft2\n\nAdded 7 golden cases filling out previously thin FFT coverage (each\noperation had \u22641 case):\n- irfft len-8 round-trip from rfft output\n- hfft N=4 from 3-complex hermitian input (8, -4, 0, 0)\n- ihfft len-6 and len-8 against numpy oracle values\n- rfft2 2x4 and irfft2 round-trip pair\n- ifft2 from fft2(2x2) must return the original real input\n\nRegenerated fft_differential_report.json artifact.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
